    `digital_health_rpm_program_enrollment_id` BIGINT COMMENT 'Foreign key linking to digital_health.digital_health_rpm_program_enrollment. Business justification: rpm_enrollment is a completely siloed table containing only its PK with no inbound or outbound FK. It is described as RPM program enrollment and alert thresholds, which is the same business concept ',
